column5: Well I thought I would give it a try,so anyone that is playing or is on it whats next after I register for a game? Will it just put me in a game? Seem lost sort of.LOL

Brian. Click on the play money tab. Then select the "All" button and just scroll down and pick a room from there. You'll have to start out in the 5/10 rooms. I enjoy playing there. Let me know if you need more help.
I was playing the free entry through the beer store Dan. Im out already.LOL  Pretty cool though. I got one more free try.LOL  Thanks for the reply
